Generic dual-database migration environment.

Preferred commands:
- `uv run alembic -c src/alembic_capture.ini upgrade head`
- `uv run alembic -c src/alembic_serving.ini upgrade head`

`ALEMBIC_DB_TARGET=capture|serving` is still supported for generic tooling, but the target-specific ini files are the
safe default because they keep capture and serving revision paths separate.
